snippet.title: Raid of Regions - Announcement Trailer (Early stage)
snippet.description:
"Intelligence Royale. Intense, insane."
Raid of Regions is an Intel Royale shooter game which is still under development. The proposed schedule of Close Alpha is starting from August to September. To learn more, please visit: http://www.raidofregions.com/press-announce-01

To register the Close Alpha: http://www.raidofregions.com

Please follow us on twitter @RaidOfRegions for more details.

NOTE: As the game is still in development, all game features may be subject to change.
